{"tid":103253,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾歷尼若贏意甲或轉教阿仙奴！！","createTime":"2017-02-01T08:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T12:58:07.000Z","uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f77d5a75320f6d5c7f765f3255986aab7bfd7183","tid":103253,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:01:49.000Z","msg":"艾歷尼曾經帶領AC米蘭及祖記拿到意甲冠軍，有傳他曾是車路士教頭候選人，不過最後是干地接手。<br />\n雲格仍然未和阿仙奴續約，有傳艾歷尼會是接任人選。意大利兼祖雲達斯名宿泰迪尼說，49歲的艾歷尼有可能被引誘轉投阿仙奴，如果他帶領祖記拿到意甲三連霸的話。<br />\n「如果他再贏一次意甲，絕對有可能選擇阿仙奴。阿仙奴很適合他，這是一間有趣的球會，艾歷利和它很匹配。可能他唯一顧慮的是能否幫祖記贏到歐聯，不過這個可能性較微了。」泰迪尼說。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=2b81267f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n屌帥：收雲老妖既皮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfbb0b5a8355c8aacede6c7e2065001d0eb99c0","tid":103253,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"唔識起球場 = 垃圾"},{"pid":"8461d8022799b824cb70041d85a32d925d4360a0","tid":103253,"uid":23235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"屌帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fa7c7c5a2d05872142000d9ed08f216a59a826","tid":103253,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你阿"},{"pid":"b77bcf0ca6b19c3106d5e4ed96bbe3138cc56f1c","tid":103253,"uid":45487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:58:07.000Z","msg":"險簽球員已經out左 宜家玩埋險簽教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雲加千秋萬代"}]}